node.text:
All of our cases are hand made in Canada and this is how we do it:
-
Woods Used.
Back Ground: Wenge
Axes: Walnut
Sun: padauk
Wilderness Wording: Maple
Mountains: cherry
-
After all the pieces are cut, they are laid up on 2 way adhesive and pressed through a roller to secure each piece in place.
-
Then it’s time to press the assembled wooden back in to the protective shell.
-
Next up is a final clean and inspection before it’s packaged up and shipped out to you!
-
Shop this design and more at www.KeywayDesigns.com
-
#wilderness #wildernessnation #wildernessculture #veneer #wood #CanadianMade
